WEBVTT

00:10.260 --> 00:12.172
<i>If al-Qaeda did this,
it is an act of war.</i>

00:12.304 --> 00:14.341
The FBI will collaborate
with the Yemen government

00:14.431 --> 00:16.218
<i>and make
as small a footprint as possible.</i>

00:16.308 --> 00:18.174
- Who the fuck's in charge here?
- I am.

00:18.936 --> 00:19.926
Who are you?

00:27.236 --> 00:29.979
He's saying that
if you want to know about the house,

00:30.072 --> 00:33.361
talk to Quso or long name.

00:33.742 --> 00:36.029
You give me reason, I give you Quso.

00:36.245 --> 00:37.952
I need you to clear a path for us.

00:38.205 --> 00:41.323
Seventeen dead Americans!
Their blood's gonna be on your hands.

00:46.421 --> 00:48.663
Ask him
if it's for a guy named Khallad.

00:55.681 --> 00:58.298
I found about the man
you want. Khallad.

00:58.392 --> 01:01.430
I'm having a bit of a problem here,
with one of your guys.

01:01.562 --> 01:03.178
<i>Truth is, I'm in sort of a bind.</i>

01:03.438 --> 01:05.349
I thought you said
his girlfriend's name was Liz.

01:05.482 --> 01:06.893
<i>The one I met was named Liz.</i>

01:07.025 --> 01:10.018
Well, you'd better tell her
the truth about your wife.

01:10.279 --> 01:12.145
That problem we recently discussed?

01:15.409 --> 01:17.776
- Our problem.
- It's being taken care of.

01:22.833 --> 01:25.416
<i>I want to rely on you</i>

01:25.669 --> 01:28.662
to fix things for us in America.

01:29.131 --> 01:30.417
I'm at your service.

